The homework is finished on CentOS 7. Following are the deliveries as requested.

hosts - the virtual host settings under the path /etc/hosts on my local machine
default.conf - Nginx virtual host config which is under the path /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf on CentOS 7
index.php - the PHP code to show phpinfo
php.ini - the PHP config which is under the path /etc/php.ini on CentOS 7.
README - this file.
ScreenShot.jpg - the screen shot of the phpinfo page. The complete content is in additional/phpinfo.html
